# NSN 组件概览 (index.md)

direction: right

CLI: "main.rs CLI"
CFG: "Figment Config"
REG: "Machine Registration"
MC: "MultiControlPlane"
MG: "MultiGatewayManager"
ST: "AppState" { shape: cylinder }
API: "Monitor API"
PROM: "Prometheus"
TEL: "telemetry::init"

CLI -> CFG
CFG -> REG
REG -> MC
REG -> MG
MC -> ST
MG -> ST
ST -> API
ST -> PROM
TEL -> PROM
